e</guid></item><item><title>随着比特币跌幅加深，加密货币清算额突破 10 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-tumbles-below-70-000-for-first-time-in-two-months</link><description>比特币情绪恶化在过去 24 小时内引发了近 15 亿美元的加密货币清算，因为最大的数字资产跌至两个月低点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4GS.zfV6DYs/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 07:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-tumbles-below-70-000-for-first-time-in-two-months</guid></item><item><title>来自 AZ 的重要加密术语列表</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-02/crypto-slang-meaning-fomo-dats-rug-pull-sniping-diamond-hands-and-more</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从空投到僵尸，这里有一个关于区分普通人和真正信徒的术语和行话的简明指南。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/imQaskDwwnGA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 09:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-02/crypto-slang-meaning-fomo-dats-rug-pull-sniping-diamond-hands-and-more</guid></item></channel></rss>